Name: ACCL
Specifications: Phase: Single ; Gen (Dg) Current Rating (A): 6 ; Mains (Eb) Current Rating (A): 30
Key_Features: Low Power Consumption , Longer Life - 25,000 Electrical Operations , Utilisation Category AC22A (IEC 60947-3) & AC32A (IEC 60947-6) , Unique Contactor Based Technology, Break Before Make Changeover Contact With Higher Air gap , Overload Indication on GENSET Side by LED and BEEP , Auto Reset Facility , Conditional Short Circuit Current Capacity 5kA , Compact Design , IS/IEC Certified
Full_Description: ACCL (Automatic Changeover & Current Limiter) offers a controlled and seamless transition from one power source to another while limiting the current on the Generator side
Short_Description: Automatically switch between two or more power sources based on predefined conditions
